Package semsim.definitions

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    OtherKBconstants
    A set of constants for working with SemSim models
    ReferenceOntologies
    Class that provides methods for working with the preferred ontologies used to annotate SemSim models.
    SBMLconstants
    Convenience sets and mappings for working with SBML models
    SemSimRelations
    Constants and functions for working with relations (AKA predicates or qualifiers) in SemSim models
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    PropertyType
    Enumeration of the main types of physical properties represented in biosimulation models.
    RDFNamespace
    Enumeration of various RDF namespaces used in biosimulation modeling formats.
    ReferenceOntologies.OntologyDomain
    Enumeration that delineates which ontologies should be used for the components of SemSim model annotations.
    ReferenceOntologies.ReferenceOntology
    Enumeration of the various ReferenceOntologies used in SemSim model annotation.
    SemSimRelations.SemSimRelation  
    SemSimRelations.StructuralRelation
    A type of SemSimRelation for establishing structural relationships between SemSim physical entities.
    SemSimTypes
    Enum and functions for the different types of objects used in SemSim models
